Disney is also doing more to make existing Infinity toys more useful, with a new 3-D Toy Box Hub that includes games in a variety of genres, including racing, farming and platformers. Toy Box Takeover is one of these, offering action-adventure gameplay, and Toy Box Speedway is the aforementioned kart racer, which is a smart way to leverage this IP with a game type that has proven immensely addictive when paired with familiar characters.


